Texts.Chs: 给你的^red;凯文老爷^reset;带200份^orange;在棍子上的婴儿脑袋^reset;
Texts.Eng: Bring ^red;Kevin, your overlord^reset; 200 ^orange;Baby Heads on Sticks^reset;

Texts.Chs: 谢谢你，莱斯特。 这次我真的有^orange;好东西^reset;给你！我保证！
Texts.Eng: Many thanks, Lester. This time I have an ^orange;honestly good^reset; thing for you! Promise!

Texts.Chs: 你有没有想过冰箱里能装下多少个婴儿头？我知道！我们来看看，好吗？如果你能收集的话...200个在棍子上的婴儿脑袋，谢谢茄子。
Texts.Eng: You ever wonder how many ^orange;baby heads^reset; you can fit in a refrigerator? I do! Let's find out, shall we? If you were to gather say...200 ^orange;baby heads on sticks^reset; I'd be ever so thankful.
